{"tid":268963,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好再諗幾時先出到pool，我浪費左一段4年既感情","createTime":"2017-06-03T11:47:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-04T16:28:45.000Z","uid":47480,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e2f4575af180ccb7c8c3e42fd82bbda6a77c885b","tid":268963,"uid":47480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T11:47:03.000Z","msg":"曾經有一個好好既機會擺左係我面前，我冇好好把握，到最後佢粒聲唔出消失左，我再搵唔返佢，每晚諗返起一齊既日子，一齊睇戲，一齊散步，一齊溫書，一齊左4年，突然間冇左佢，先意識到佢對自己有幾咁重要。<br />\n<br />\n你知我冇記性，有咩重要野都係你幫我Mark低，凍會提我著衫，落雨提我帶遮，生日/相識記念日冇一次都冇同你慶祝，你都冇嬲過。<br />\n<br />\n你知我窮，咁多年黎冬天一件外套都冇買過比俾你著，你冇出聲，但有一次我捉住你等車，知你一直都係捱緊凍，我真係好廢。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解你粒聲唔出走左去呀!!! 冇左你我仲點生存落去呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 邊條粉皮拎左我部電話，限你兩日內交返出黎"},{"pid":"a849b3c85ce32199b2633ab12d3de916fe4274c2","tid":268963,"uid":7430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T11:48:16.000Z","msg":"On9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"704c80aa1d22d4aa8326d5f98cbc2b0a612021ec","tid":268963,"uid":47480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T11:49:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>On9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockq